PODKATCHER - THE KDE PODCASTING CLIENT
--------------------------------------

What is podKatcher?
-------------------

podKatcher is an end-user desktop client for podcasting. 
The software will provide functionality to find, search, 
subscribe, archive, play back and create audio and video 
podcasts.


Optaining podKatcher
--------------------

Further information and the latest release can be obtained 
at http://www.podkatcher.org


Requirements
------------

Running podKatcher requires a recent KDE installation.


Documentation
-------------

Documentation can be found at http://www.podkatcher.org


Installation instructions
-------------------------

See the INSTALL file


